title: Father Brown - Radio Dramas
description:
13 X 30 mins

Unlike the recent run of ridiculous Father Brown dramas on BBC TV, these are dramatisations of the original Chesterton short stories, all set in the correct period, with Andrew Sachs as the eponymous Priest cum detective. Make for entertaining listening.


New posting of a previously posted torrent, following the loss of the original torrent after an HDD failure.
